gksu-polkit: gksu-polkit (gksu-polkit GNOME sudo)
gksu-polkit: 
gksu-polkit: This is the new generation of gksu, a simple utility to run programs
gksu-polkit: as root, even in X-based environments. This version uses the new
gksu-polkit: libgksu-polkit library, which uses PolicyKit for authorization
gksu-polkit: purposes and a D-Bus service to actually perform the work.
gksu-polkit:
gksu-polkit: http://live.gnome.org/gksu
